Reference link: #link("https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/42434849")[zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/42434849]

Execute the following command:

```bash
sudo tlmgr conf texmf OSFONTDIR /System/Library/Assets/com_apple_MobileAsset_Font4/
```

Here, `Assets` and `com_apple_MobileAsset_Font4` change with the system version. For example, the corresponding folders for the current `Ventura` version are `AssetsV2` and `com_apple_MobileAsset_Font7`.

After executing the above command, luatex will be able to recognize system fonts. To cancel this, execute the following command:

```bash
sudo tlmgr conf texmf --delete OSFONTDIR
```
